{
  "stem": "1491.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we look at them like crazy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They walked in, they marched in, the whole army, men and women.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw them going under the showers together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were looking at it that we couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then after they cleaned up, they decide-- luckily I had a friend over there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] She's going to tell them to stop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But who's going to let her in?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, so-- so anyway, good I had a friend, a man who was taking care of me and my mother.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was much older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somehow he was like our-- what shall I say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was taking care of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he makes-- so when they came, they have to washed up, they start raping women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And women were jumping, hiding, you can't imagine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But luckily, we had him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he hid us in someplace and he protect us from it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we weren't affected.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were raping women right and left who could hardly walk, who were sick, who were from concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they wanted us to work in the hospitals with the wounded soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you know, always some people become like leaders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They said, go to town, take the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What do-- these women can hardly walk, can hardly breathe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they emptied out all the warehouses, whatever food was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had nothing to eat, absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they said go to town, knock on the doors, and that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In groups like that, and walked from door to door, begging for a potato, or piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that Czechoslovakians are very good people, very good natured people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they tried to help us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
